<div><ExampleComponent ExampleCode="@(new StrokeLineJoinArcsExample())" /></div>

<h5>Opacity</h5>
<p>To change the opacity of the stroke, assign value to Opacity property:</p>
<div><ExampleComponent ExampleCode="@(new StrokeOpacityExample())" /></div>

